ik der Blindheit und des Nichtwissens und beschreiben diese in ihren film- und kulturgeschichtlichen Zusammenhängen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aAllgemeine Literaturwissenschaft. 4aAnglistik. 4aDavid Lynch. 4aKultur. 4aLiteratur. 4aMedien. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aNichtwissen. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aBritish Studies.  aCulture.  aGeneral Literature Studies.  aLiterature.  aMedia Studies.  aMedia.1 aBerressem, Hanjo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrittnacher, Hans Richard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGeisenhanslüke, Achim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGeisenhanslüke, Achim, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKaul, Susanne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLiebrand, Claudia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOverthun, Rasmus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOverthun, Rasmus, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aPalmier, Jean-Pierre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchmitt, Mark, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aShelton, Catherine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSteltz, Christian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2010-2013z9783110370